        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=POE-Component-IRC-Plugin-Syntax-Highlight-CSS

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/POE-Component-IRC-Plugin-Syntax-Highlight-CSS

    CPAN Ratings
